## 2. Module Breakdown

The system is decomposed into **12 vertical modules**. Each has its own routes, services, DB tables, and UI surface.

### 2.1 Core Modules

1. **Identity & Access** вҖ” auth, users, roles, RBAC, password reset, session management
2. **Members (Clients)** вҖ” profile, memberships, payments, attendance, body metrics
3. **Trainers** вҖ” profile, schedule, payouts, performance metrics
4. **Memberships & Plans** вҖ” plan catalog, subscriptions, freezes, renewals
5. **Payments & Billing** вҖ” manual entry, gateway integration, invoices, receipts, dues
6. **Classes & Bookings** вҖ” group classes, recurring schedule, capacity, waitlists
7. **Personal Training** вҖ” 1:1 session booking, conflict detection, cancellation policy
8. **Attendance** вҖ” QR check-in, manual override, geofencing (optional)
9. **Notifications** вҖ” multi-channel orchestrator (email/WhatsApp/SMS/push/in-app)
10. **Reports & Analytics** вҖ” revenue, retention, trainer performance, churn, exports
11. **Settings & Branding** вҖ” gym info, currency, tax, business hours, holidays
12. **Audit & Activity** вҖ” every mutation logged for compliance and debugging

