### 7.5 Class booking flow (Member)

1. **Browse** вҖ” calendar week-view, filter by trainer/type/time-of-day
2. **Detail sheet** вҖ” class info, capacity (12/15), trainer bio, "Book"
3. **Confirm** вҖ” uses included sessions or charges drop-in fee
4. **Manage** вҖ” Bookings tab; cancel respects policy (e.g., >2h prior = free, else 1 session forfeit)
5. **Check-in** вҖ” QR code shown 30min before; scanner at gym door

### 7.6 Empty states & micro-interactions

- All lists have intentional empty states with an illustrated icon + 1 line copy + 1 CTA. (v2 already does this on payments вҖ” extend everywhere.)
- Skeleton loaders, not spinners, on dashboards.
- Optimistic UI for booking/cancel/check-in.

